stinct Domains of Prehistoric Gene Flow in Europe |url=http://www.familytreedna.com/pdf/DNA.RootsiHaplogroupISpread.pdf |journal=American Journal of Human Genetics |volume=75 |issue=1 |pages=128–137 |pmid=15162323 |pmc=1181996 |postscript=. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090619180737/http://www.familytreedna.com/pdf/DNA.RootsiHaplogroupISpread.pdf |archivedate=2009年6月19日 |accessdate=2014年1月30日 }}</ref>
，其中Y染色体{{tsl|en|Haplogroup I-M253|单倍型类群 I1 (Y-DNA)|单倍型类群 I1}}與[[日耳曼人|日耳曼人]]相關<ref name=genographic>[https://genographic.nationalgeographic.com/atlas.html Genographic Project of National Geographic]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name=newphylo>"New Phylogenetic Relationships for Y-chromosome Haplogroup I: Reappraising its Phylogeography and Prehistory," Rethinking the Human Evolution, Mellars P, Boyle K, Bar-Yosef O, Stringer C, Eds. McDonald Institute for Archaeological Research, Cambridge, UK, 2007, pp. 33–42 by Underhill PA, Myres NM, Rootsi S, Chow CT, Lin AA, Otillar RP, King R, Zhivotovsky LA, Balanovsky O, Pshenichnov A, Ritchie KH, Cavalli-Sforza LL, Kivisild T, Villems R, Woodward SR</ref>；[[印度次大陸|印度次大陸]]和[[中亞|中亞]]及[[高加索|高加索]]還有Y染色体{{tsl|en|Haplogroup R2|单倍型类群 R2 (Y-DNA)|单倍型类群 R2}}，其中至少佔90%的人居住於印度次大陸<ref name="manoukian">Manoukian, Jean-Grégoire (2006), "[http://www.ethnoancestry.com/index_files/index_data/Haplogroup_R2_Manoukian.pdf A Synthesis of Haplogroup R2 - 2006] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ethnoancestry.com/index_files/index_data/Haplogroup_R2_Manoukian.pdf |date=20151001014558 }}."</ref>，在[[西孟加拉邦|西孟加拉邦]]的{{link-en|洛得人|Lodha people}}、[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]海岸的[[泰盧固人|泰盧固人]]和[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]的[[僧伽羅人|僧伽羅人]]中有密集出現。

